Installation:

Requirements: 

Python 3
Virtualenvwrapper
SQLite

Create a virtual environment for the application and activate it

mkvirtualenv microblog

Then in the folder where this README file is, run the command

pip install -r requirements.txt

This will install Flask and all the application's requirements

Initialise the database

flask db init

Run the migrations

flask db migrate 

Upgrade the database (apply the migrations)

flask db upgrade

Then run the application with

flask run

Visit the site at 

http://localhost:5000/
